This sets _listeners.play = arrow1, _listeners.pause = arrow2, _listeners.seeked = arrow3. Then after unbind, they should all be deleted.

But wait, the test "bind/unbind 反复调用不会累积 listener" passed! That uses `bindVideoEvents` and `unbindVideoEvents` repeatedly. So the implementation works there.

Let me look more carefully at the failing test... actually wait, my test #3 (which failed) does:
```js
