## 实施过程踩的坑 (1 个)

**1. typo 修 unbindVideoEvents 时把 `'seeked'` 写成 `'seek'`** — 第一遍写代码时把 `removeEventListener('seeked', ...)` 写成了 `removeEventListener('seek', ...)` (一字母之差). 测试 1 失败暴露: "解绑后 emit seeked 仍触发 send (1 !== 0)". Debug 发现后立刻改回 `'seeked'`. 教训: 字符串字面量, **实施完**跑 `npm test` 立刻验证, 不能只靠 type-check 主观判断.

**已修**: 改后 112/112 pass.

---

## 关键改动说明

### 改动 1: app.js peer.on('open')

```js
// 改前 (绕过状态机, UI 脱钩根因)
this.peer.on('open', (id) => {
  updateLocalStatus('等待对方加入...', 'waiting');
  ...
});

// 改后 (走状态机, 触发 listener → UI)
this.peer.on('open', (id) => {
  if (typeof recomputeRoomState === 'function') {
    recomputeRoomState();
  } else {
    updateLocalStatus('等待对方加入...', 'waiting');  // 防御性 fallback
  }
  ...
});
```

`recomputeRoomState` 是同 IIFE 内的函数, 类方法可通过 lexical scope 访问.

### 改动 2: sync-engine.js bindVideoEvents + unbindVideoEvents

```js
constructor(...) {
  ...
  this._onPlay = null;     // stored ref for unbind
  this._onPause = null;
  this._onSeeked = null;
  this.bindVideoEvents();
}

bindVideoEvents() {
  this._onPlay = () => this.maybeSend('play');
  this._onPause = () => this.maybeSend('pause');
  this._onSeeked = () => this.maybeSend('seek');
  this.video.addEventListener('play', this._onPlay);
  this.video.addEventListener('pause', this._onPause);
  this.video.addEventListener('seeked', this._onSeeked);
}

unbindVideoEvents() {  // 幂等
  if (this._onPlay) this.video.removeEventListener('play', this._onPlay);
  if (this._onPause) this.video.removeEventListener('pause', this._onPause);
  if (this._onSeeked) this.video.removeEventListener('seeked', this._onSeeked);  // 注意: 是 'seeked' 不是 'seek'
  this._onPlay = null;
  this._onPause = null;
  this._onSeeked = null;
}
```

### 改动 3: app.js exitRoom + startSession 加 unbindVideoEvents

```js
function exitRoom() {
  if (!connMgr) return;
  if (connMgr.engine) connMgr.engine.unbindVideoEvents();  // ← 新增 (在 destroy 之前)
  connMgr.destroy();
  ...
}

function startSession(isInitiator, targetRoomId) {
  if (connMgr) {
    if (connMgr.engine) connMgr.engine.unbindVideoEvents();  // ← 新增
    connMgr.destroy();
  }
  ...
}
```

### 改动 4: build.yml 加 build-mac-debug job

- `on.workflow_dispatch.inputs` 加 `build_type` choice (debug | release, default release)
- 新增 `build-mac-debug` job:
  - `if: github.event.inputs.build_type == 'debug' && startsWith(github.ref, 'refs/heads/main')`
  - `runs-on: macos-latest`
  - `npx electron-builder --mac --arm64 --config.mac.identity=null` (ad-hoc 签名)
